race.comment: CRUISE OR LOSE (2) was below best at her last start when 7th at this track following a second place finish (18.60) there two back. Has a good record here at this journey. Rates on top in this line up. REDSHIFT FOXTROT (7) held her own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only 1.3 lengths (17.65) behind Cundle Zack at Taree Super Track. Will give a great sight again. PUMPKIN EATER (8) has missed the placings at her last couple but was in the money three back when second (23.40) at this track in a Mix 3/4. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. ARTHUR CHANCE (4) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to turn the form around.
